{"tid":1784564,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全民black bloc真係好重要","createTime":"2019-12-15T17:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T04:31:43.000Z","uid":189146,"like":68,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1a56f67944cb6ee3582c17408b4d7aeb8ba937d2","tid":1784564,"uid":189146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T17:59:01.000Z","msg":"平時勇武出去一定係black bloc<br />\n有啲和理非會因為驚被誤會係勇武而唔想著黑衫<br />\n有啲連口罩都唔敢戴<br />\n但係和理非如果都着埋全黑就可以掩護到手足<br />\n依家勇武越拉越少<br />\n有掩護會無咁易被狗認得出<br />\n<br />\n我自己就日日帶住件u記薄風褸出街<br />\n百幾蚊又可以摺到好細塞落個袋仔到<br />\n希望大家可以做多少少幫下手足<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3b686404e69d278193358970218c2ade2a01304","tid":1784564,"uid":263349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:01:17.000Z","msg":"可能要搞個 和理非black bloc 日 宣傳下"},{"pid":"14ddc331a6c9d3d4b2ab7c54e05680b691400352","tid":1784564,"uid":307619,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T18:02:47.000Z","msg":"認同<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;<br />\nsorry p牌仔借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n男銷售員 6 月涉推跌六旬男子致死被控<span style=\"color: red;\">謀殺</span>　控方近半年仍未能確定死因<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776775\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776775</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong>手足無證無據都生豬肉坐咗半年<br />\n又話手足唔係condom？<br />\n就快生豬肉到2020年<br />\n可唔可以幫手關注下呢單野<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SGaZPt9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSGaZPt9.jpg&h=6915346d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4bb38c5086a9aaf2922be8684b84cab461420ee1","tid":1784564,"uid":189146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a3b686404e69d278193358970218c2ade2a01304","tid":178